author: Journal Inquirer Staff
title: Cheney Tech remains undefeated
text:
Cheney Tech remains undefeated By Journal Inquirer Staff   
Holding only a 7-6 lead at halftime, the Cheney Tech football team decided to let Ramon Gracia go to work. 
Before the third quarter was over, Gracia had thrown a 79-yard touchdown pass to to Steven Martinez, and a 20-yard scoring strike to Jeremee Burgos. The Beavers rattled off 26 unanswered points en route to a 33-20 victory over Vinal Tech/East Hampton/Goodwin Tech at Palmer Field in Middletown on Saturday.
